Packages 
Package Description
com.epam.finaltask.command
Contains interfaces for commands used by servlets.
com.epam.finaltask.command.impl
This package contains command layer implementation classes.
com.epam.finaltask.connectionpool
Contains connection pool and classes required for it to work.
com.epam.finaltask.controller
Contains servlets of the application.
com.epam.finaltask.dao
Provides interfaces to create and use DAOs and create connection manager.
com.epam.finaltask.dao.impl
Provides implementations for dao interfaces, dao and connection manager factories.
com.epam.finaltask.entity
Contains application entities.
com.epam.finaltask.filter
Contains web filters used by application.
com.epam.finaltask.service
Provides services containing application business logic.
com.epam.finaltask.tag
Contains custom jsp tags.
com.epam.finaltask.util
Contains hash generator and it's factory interfaces, classes with application constants
com.epam.finaltask.util.impl
Contains implementations for com.epam.finaltask.util package interfaces.
com.epam.finaltask.validation
Provides validation classes.
